She's right in there.

7
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,380
The switch for the passageway

8
00:03:48,870 --> 00:03:49,570
is right there.

9
00:03:51,910 --> 00:03:52,380
Go ahead.

10
00:04:38,830 --> 00:04:39,660
Find another entrance.

11
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:28,900
