25
00:06:00,510 --> 00:06:01,410
You're a physician.

26
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,610
Can't you tell I'm pregnant?

27
00:06:09,510 --> 00:06:10,340
No way.

28
00:06:10,830 --> 00:06:12,140
Hai couldn't have...

29
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:13,100
Take my pulse

30
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,580
